article.description: — Michael Forrest scored 14 points as Florida Atlantic edged Charlotte 74-69 on Saturday.
article.headline: Forrest scores 14 to carry FAU past Charlotte 74-69
article.linkText: Forrest scores 14 to carry FAU past Charlotte 74-69
article.story: CHARLOTTE, N.C. -- — Michael Forrest scored 14 points as Florida Atlantic edged Charlotte 74-69 on Saturday. Alijah Martin had 13 points and seven rebounds for Florida Atlantic (16-13, 9-7 Conference USA), which ended its four-game losing streak. Jahmir Young had 26 points for the 49ers (15-13, 8-8). Clyde Trapp Jr. added 13 points. Jackson Threadgill had 10 points. The Owls improved to 2-0 against the 49ers this season. Florida Atlantic defeated Charlotte 96-67 on Jan. 17. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
